skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: norris jokes unofficial
des:
This skill is not sponsored or endorsed by Chuck Norris. Jokes are retrieved from the Internet Chuck Norris Database - http://www.icndb.com.

Alexa will tell you a Chuck Norris joke. You can also select different types of jokes with the following phrases:

Alexa, ask Norris Jokes Unofficial to tell me a geeky joke.
Alexa, ask Norris Jokes Unofficial for a joke about {First name here}.
Alexa, ask Norris Jokes Unofficial for a {First name} joke.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
